# Arnie uses the Anthropic API directly from the browser via claude.ai's built-in proxy.
# If you are self-hosting this app outside of claude.ai, you will need to:
# 1. Set up a backend proxy to protect your API key
# 2. Replace the fetch URL in src/App.jsx with your proxy endpoint
# 3. Add your key here and load it server-side only — never expose it in the browser

# VITE_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_key_here
